Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:29.92,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)}4月12日 Oasis(綠洲)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為摩托車修理的比較慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最初我就覺得她不像好人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是那個女人就以此為借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽還沒升起來的時候就沖過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一文錢都沒給
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開著摩托車猛沖 把橋都弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我店里的客人 損失全部由我承擔了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么豈有此理的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒錯 是Michiko Malandro吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽前臺的話說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是去Osso了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Osso？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好幾個人聽到她說 要去見Satoshi Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一路很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格也好 味道也好 差勁到家的超級飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連著光顧了3天3夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的話只有一個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長的只有頭發嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不想回去的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那對人妖兄弟耍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Seria那個大媽勒索 搞得身無分文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！ 不要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到的只是 800克滿是牛筋的牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些都過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以為我演奏一曲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,funky風格的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的噪音與致命的游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！ 居然擅自行動！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴了 雖然是擅自行動 我要喝果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這口氣是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽Michiko說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你為什么這么生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不說我怎么能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就直說了 你是怎么想的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 毀壞了很多東西 不付錢就跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看個屁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作出那樣的事情 你心里是怎么想的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Michiko的作為而流淚的人有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那個修理鋪的大叔 你不該恐嚇他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很討厭這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嘛 是成年人之間的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用扳手去交涉嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的行為都討厭 我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡快回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不許一個人在街上亂逛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\pos(200,200)}愛之病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲喲 我帶來了 奶油可可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你丫 怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這臺狗屎機器！ 我一次都沒贏過！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你這么說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫知道我是誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Satoshi先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是Monstro Preto(黑色怪物)的老大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老子惹毛了豈不是很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲喲 把屁眼挖挖干凈聽好 你這個土包子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸掉的錢和預定會贏的錢 一共2000Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 這個家伙的Super Stick就要捅進你的屁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！ 我馬上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到過Satoshi Batista嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他在這個城市的什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要拔槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不要那么拘束嘛 Pogo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事情！ 您居然大駕光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次那件事情 電話里更本談不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的Satoshi君 更本不能接受那樣的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的有理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有收到你們的孝敬錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了一個自稱是Satoshi的人 就輕易把錢交出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請不要在意 請繼續用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你能讓我見見那個自稱是Satoshi的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我會去收拾他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊？ Pogo說的Satoshi君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等！ Satoshi先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 以為老子是閃閃發光的巧克力豆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在這里做生意是托的誰的福啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Satoshi先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 別磨磨嘰嘰的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拿錢出來 還是卵蛋被踩爆 你自己挑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聽聽卵蛋被踩爆時的美妙聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢... 我付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 兄弟 我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 感動的淚流滿面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么立刻就生氣 也不聽聽我的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了叫Satoshi的人 于是在后面跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么地方？ Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Estela
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開口 就會吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想過 我們兩還是不要在一起為好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看見Michiko的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承諾過 要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么 即使你忘記這個承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pogo 你說過這個飯店是四星級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安保是零星級嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闖空門的那些混蛋 大搖大擺地就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話 說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡覺 別睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就按安排我們去最好的套房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pogo 給我們安排保安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 費用也由你出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)}四月13日 Estela飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說辦不到 Pogo那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說什么 宰了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個禿頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是不是沒搞清楚什么叫保安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pogo那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi Batista在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 平民區的總統 Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們早就露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要流一身汗再回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你爽到升天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要試試 很爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣 我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超絕! Jesus！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對我這如同耶穌一般的下巴你能下的了手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 要流出來了 愛汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我真的迷上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 敢過來就揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 請再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個閃電一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心都被電焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 去叫出租車 三秒以內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marquee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是那個黑色怪物Montro Preto
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經包圍了飯店周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 Davy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我們完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒說完呢 別掛電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了哦 忘記我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡小白臉的Michi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你在Vermelha大搞了一場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來見Satoshi的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 你失望了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓那邊的總統閣下接一下電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Shinsuke 能讓我見見Satoshi嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 我可不會白告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不缺錢 那個要做個游戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫說什么 Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫知道我的個性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能堂堂正正地出來談談嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要 很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 只有憑武力去問出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 我的包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只說自己是Satoshi 沒說是Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們很強所以是黑色怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是自稱Montro Preto而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都沒有假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還沒搞清你的對手是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的怪物 他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩游戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 能放過這邊的冒牌Satoshi嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們拿的錢全部奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我絕對會贏 那時讓我見Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是條件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 必須全員參加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會贏是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就放過那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會讓你見最想見的Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒有問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我說明一下規則
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就乘電車來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安地到達我這就算獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名為“Non-stop換乘游戲”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過電車會從什么方向來 并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一下 一旦搞錯了就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人會毫不留情地射擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能甩掉追擊回歸正確路線 也可以饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 現在開始我要說明線路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只說一遍 拼命記錄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 現在附近就有前往Obelisk站的電車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘這個電車 向西去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parque Triangulo在中途換乘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是Solao吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前走一點就是Santa Eatrela站...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Mercgado Central站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里換乘前往Santa Eatrela
